# Task 4 - Currency Converter

This Java program is a **Currency Converter** that allows users to convert an amount from one currency to another using fixed or real-time exchange rates (if API integration is added).

## âœ… Features

- User can select:
  - Base currency (e.g., USD, INR, EUR)
  - Target currency
- Accepts input amount for conversion
- Converts the amount using a predefined exchange rate
- Displays the result in target currency
- Can be extended to use real-time exchange rates via an API

